@let me explain studio. You have encouraged me to be a youtuber! No, not an animator.
(And I did dounloud the software and all that like you.) And man, you animators deserve more credit and respect.
And I mean it. It's like people when they make a book but people boo at it because they wanted romance or something.
(I am one of those people on wattpad. My book website. I am a brony.) But I decided to get a video editing app
So I can do it myself. Now, I am a tech wiz, but it is going to take me a while to get used to it. But, I guess you did the same.
But, me being me, I want to follow in your right foot step while my other foot Is following somebody else's. So I can kill two passions with one website.
Love your animator style, and the fact that you don't make mouths, makes your vids 110% better. Like grumit. Love the facial features too!
So, yeah. I'm doing this to hopefully make a living off of it. Now it will take like 100 years, I know, but i will do my best. See you lata
